structure properly.

1034
00:53:29.696 --> 00:53:31.197
[Indistinct chatter]

1035
00:53:31.282 --> 00:53:34.181
[♪]

1036
00:53:37.535 --> 00:53:39.369
[Woman] Excuse me.

1037
00:53:39.453 --> 00:53:41.622
Are you a presenter
here tonight?

1038
00:53:44.270 --> 00:53:45.355
I am.

1039
00:53:46.329 --> 00:53:47.993
[Woman] And what makes you think

1040
00:53:48.078 --> 00:53:50.713
you can interrupt
this presentation?

1041
00:53:50.798 --> 00:53:54.301
I have come with a prototype
for a quantum fusion process.

1042
00:53:57.888 --> 00:53:59.306
[Chatter stops]

1043
00:54:13.825 --> 00:54:15.202
Do it.

1044
00:54:20.286 --> 00:54:22.163
[Electric pulsating]

1045
00:54:27.251 --> 00:54:29.545
[Crowd murmuring]

1046
00:55:04.205 --> 00:55:06.332
[Electric pulsating]

1047
